Questions : Write a query to obtain a histogram of tweets posted per user in 2022. 
            The output should include the tweet count per user as the bucket and the number of Twitter users who fall into that bucket.



select tweet_cnt, count(*) from (
select user_id, count(tweet_id) as tweet_cnt
from tweets
where extract(year from tweet_date) = 2022 
group by 1) as sub
group by 1;
